</head>

<body data-spy="scroll" data-target="#navbar-example">
<% include templates/nav.ejs%>

<div class="container">
    <section id="one">
        <h3>Plant Profiles</h3>
        <br>
        <p>This page profiles plant taxa which may be employed in the rehabilitation of mine sites. The distributions of plants are included so you can ascertain the relevance of various taxa to a site. Australia's Virtual Herbarium can be further engaged for this purpose and it is worth some time learning how to use this valuable resource.</p>
        <br>
        <p style="color: red">*This list is a work in progress</p>

        <div id="profiles" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">

            <%  for(let i=0; i<profiles.length ;i++)  {   %>
            <!-- <%= profiles[i].name %> -->
